<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>
    No autorizado
  </title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/favicon.ico">
  <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest/dist/umd/lucide.js"></script>
  <link href="/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #fcfcfc;
      height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .error-card {
      border: none;
      border-top: 5px solid #dc3545;
      /* Línea roja superior */
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .status-code {
      font-size: 4rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #dee2e6;
      line-height: 1;
    }

    .message-box {
      background-color: #fff5f5;
      border-left: 4px solid #dc3545;
      padding: 15px;
      font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
      word-wrap: break-word;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-md-7 col-lg-5">
        <div class="card error-card shadow-lg">
          <div class="card-body p-5">
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4">
              <div class="status-code">
                <%= status %>
              </div>
              <div class="icon">
                <i data-lucide="circle-alert" style="width: 48px; height: 48px;" class="text-danger"></i>
              </div>
            </div>

            <h3 class="h4 fw-bold">¡Ups! Algo salió mal</h3>
            <p class="text-muted">Se ha producido un error al procesar tu solicitud. Aquí tienes los detalles:</p>

            <div class="message-box my-4">
              <strong>Detalle:</strong><br>
              <span class="text-danger">
                <%= mensaje %>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-center mt-4 text-muted small">ID del Error: <%= Date.now() %>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    lucide.createIcons();
  </script>
  <script src="/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>

</body>

</html>